<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 09:11:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>上海证券交易所终止对先正达IPO申请的审核</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shanghai-stock-exchange-terminates-review-syngentas-ipo-application-2024-03-29/</link><description>瑞士农化公司先正达申请撤回上市计划后，上海证券交易所周五表示，终止对先正达首次公开发行股票申请的审核。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 08:57:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shanghai-stock-exchange-terminates-review-syngentas-ipo-application-2024-03-29/</guid></item><item><title>习近平旧讲话引发中国货币宽松猜测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/old-xi-jinping-speech-sparks-china-monetary-easing-speculation-2024-03-29/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平几个月前的讲话中的一句话引发了人们的猜测，即央行可能会开始大举购买政府债券以支持经济，而这是中国长期以来一直回避的刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 08:50:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/old-xi-jinping-speech-sparks-china-monetary-easing-speculation-2024-03-29/</guid></item><item><title>科威尔的早期成功证明水手队的怀疑者是错误的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/early-success-sees-kewell-prove-doubters-wrong-with-marinos-2024-03-29/</link><description>前澳大利亚前锋哈里·科威尔可能仍处于担任横滨水手队主教练的初期阵痛期，但这位欧洲冠军联赛冠军边锋已经站在了他的经验更丰富的前任都无法实现的壮举的尖端。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 07:43:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/early-success-sees-kewell-prove-doubters-wrong-with-marinos-2024-03-29/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称台湾海军总长下周将访问美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwans-navy-chief-visit-us-next-week-sources-say-2024-03-29/</link><description>六名知情人士透露，台湾海军司令唐华将从下周开始访问美国，参加军事仪式，并讨论在中国对台湾提出威胁之际如何加强双边海军合作。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 04:03:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwans-navy-chief-visit-us-next-week-sources-say-2024-03-29/</guid></item><item><title>外汇官员称中国将进一步扩大资本账户开放</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-will-further-enhance-capital-account-opening-fx-official-says-2024-03-29/</link><description>一位高级外汇监管机构周五表示，随着北京在地缘政治紧张局势加剧之际寻求吸引外国投资者，中国将让资本更容易地进出中国，并促进金融市场放松管制。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 03:21:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-will-further-enhance-capital-account-opening-fx-official-says-2024-03-29/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾表示不会屈服于“屈尊”中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-it-will-not-yield-submission-row-with-patronising-china-2024-03-29/</link><description>菲律宾国防部周五表示，菲律宾无意在南海挑衅或制造麻烦，但也不会被吓倒而保持沉默、屈服或屈服，这是其在与中国的激烈争执中最新的反抗表现。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 03:12:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-it-will-not-yield-submission-row-with-patronising-china-2024-03-29/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着第一季度的落幕，日元对假期平静持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-28/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 21:49:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>高盛和摩根士丹利赢得驳回Archegos倒闭诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/goldman-morgan-stanley-win-dismissal-lawsuits-over-archegos-collapse-2024-03-28/</link><description>周四，一名美国法官驳回了投资者的七项诉讼，这些投资者指控高盛集团和摩根士丹利存在不当行为，导致比尔·黄 (Bill Hwang) 的 360 亿美元公司 Archegos Capital Management 在 2021 年 3 月迅速倒闭。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 21:30:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/goldman-morgan-stanley-win-dismissal-lawsuits-over-archegos-collapse-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国可能很快公布禁止接收技术的中国芯片工厂名单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-may-soon-unveil-list-chinese-chip-factories-barred-receiving-tech-2024-03-28/</link><description>三名知情人士周四表示，美国正在制定一份禁止接收关键工具的先进中国芯片制造工厂名单，以便企业更容易阻止技术流入中国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 20:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-may-soon-unveil-list-chinese-chip-factories-barred-receiving-tech-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>世贸组织：中国对美国电动汽车和可再生能源税收抵免发起争议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/wto-china-initiates-dispute-over-us-tax-credits-evs-renewables-2024-03-28/</link><description>世界贸易组织周四表示，中国已就《通货膨胀削减法案》下的税收抵免启动与美国的争端磋商，以促进电动汽车和可再生能源的生产。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 15:59:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/wto-china-initiates-dispute-over-us-tax-credits-evs-renewables-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国商务部长将前往欧洲阐述电动汽车案例</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-commerce-minister-head-europe-make-ev-case-2024-03-28/</link><description>四名了解该计划的人士告诉路透社，中国商务部长将于四月前往欧洲，讨论欧盟委员会对中国电动汽车行业是否受益于不公平补贴的调查。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 12:56:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-commerce-minister-head-europe-make-ev-case-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>生产商表示，中国对澳大利亚葡萄酒征收关税将损害波尔多葡萄酒的销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-duty-clear-australian-wine-will-hurt-bordeaux-sales-producers-say-2024-03-28/</link><description>法国波尔多葡萄酒出口商占中国葡萄酒和烈酒进口总量的9%，预计在中国周四决定提高对澳大利亚葡萄酒的进口关税后，出口将迅速下降。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 11:26:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-duty-clear-australian-wine-will-hurt-bordeaux-sales-producers-say-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>报告称全球智能手机市场将于 2024 年反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/global-smartphone-market-set-rebound-2024-report-says-2024-03-28/</link><description>Counterpoint Research 周四发布的一份报告称，由于通胀缓解有助于新兴市场需求复苏，加上生成式人工智能的集成吸引买家购买高端设备，全球智能手机出货量预计今年将反弹 3%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 11:14:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/global-smartphone-market-set-rebound-2024-report-says-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉交付量面临中国经济放缓和需求疲软的打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-deliveries-face-hit-china-slowdown-soft-demand-2024-03-28/</link><description>预计特斯拉下周将报告第一季度交付量低迷，原因是其降价带来的提振作用减弱，而且这家美国汽车制造商正在应对电动汽车市场放缓中买家的激烈竞争。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 09:37:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-deliveries-face-hit-china-slowdown-soft-demand-2024-03-28/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚渴望在中国牛肉和龙虾出口障碍方面取得进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lifts-tariffs-australian-wine-bilateral-ties-recover-2024-03-28/</link><description>一名政府官员表示，澳大利亚的重点是消除一些供应商向中国出口活龙虾和牛肉的障碍，一天前北京表示将提高对澳大利亚葡萄酒的关税。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 08:27:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lifts-tariffs-australian-wine-bilateral-ties-recover-2024-03-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>